Maksym Bondarenko 
Cergy, 2016

This project will include:

FDM folder:
- Finite difference methods to solve PDE (Heat equation, BS-equation) with different types of boundary conditions

Calibration folder:
- Calibration of financial parametres: Implied volatility, Yield

Monte-Carlo folder:
- Monte-Carlo simulation of random variables to apply in share price simulation and insurance projects

Optimization folder:
- Numerical Optimization algorithms: Steepest descent, Gradient descent, Newton Algorithm, Newton-Lagrange algorithm (with constraints)
